{
  "name": "Medical Release Corruption",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Medical.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to generate a surge of twisted medical release chakra designed spread like a curse, draining all creatures in range. Select a space you can see within range. You manifest a 5-foot radius field of corruption. At the beginning of each of your turns for the duration, the size of the field grows by 5 feet.</p><p>All creature who begins their turns within the affected area or first enter the affected area on their turns, must make a Charisma saving throw. On a failed save creatures take 3d12 necrotic damage and no damage on a successful save.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the damage by 1d12.</p>",
